name: Lohikeitto
desc: Classic soup from the frigid regions. Succulent salmon is cut into chunks and cooked with fresh vegetables. Cream is added just before serving, along with other special seasonings, to create a bowl of warm, hearty chowder with a silky-smooth texture.

value.text: Restores 20% of Max HP to the selected character and regenerates 390 HP every 5s for 30s.
